text: Dihydrotestosterone butyrate, also known as androstanolone butyrate or stanolone butyrate, as well as 5α-dihydrotestosterone 17β-butanoate, is a synthetic androgen and anabolic steroid and a dihydrotestosterone ester that was never marketed. ==See also== * List of androgen esters § Dihydrotestosterone esters ==References== Category:Abandoned drugs Category:Androgens and anabolic steroids Category:Androstanes Category:Butyrate esters Category:Dihydrotestosterone esters Category:Prodrugs Category:Testosterone
title: Dihydrotestosterone butyrate
